description: Green Gelato is an indica-dominant hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Thin Mint Girl Scout Cookies and Sunset Sherbet. This strain is 40% sativa and 60% indica. Green Gelato has a rare and exotic lineage, as it is the only strain cultivated by Grow West in Maryland. Green Gelato is 18-22% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for experienced cannabis consumers.
lineage_parents: Thin Mint Girl Scout Cookies, Sunset Sherbet
